column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Thursday July 22 at 4:00 p.m.

column3: Traffic Alert for Versailles Rd near the Fayette/Woodford Co Line:
column4: Serious collision involving multiple vehicles.  The roadway is shutdown in both directions until further notice due to Police investigation.

column3: Traffic Alert for Versailles Rd near the Fayette/Woodford Co Line:
column4: Outbound traffic diverted to Man O War Blvd.  Inbound traffic diverted to Shannon Run Rd to Military Pike.

column3: Traffic Alert for Versailles Rd near the Fayette/Woodford Co Line:
column4: UPDATE 11:16 a.m.:  Outbound Versailles Rd is now open.  Inbound Versailles Rd remains shutdown.
